00:27:38.800 --> 00:27:41.560
not enough, uh, for the amount of assortment we deal with.

00:27:41.599 --> 00:27:46.520
So, um, I mean, when we think about historical assortment at Walmart, it's

00:27:46.719 --> 00:27:52.839
250 million today for, if you need two years of analysis, you know, by day.

00:27:53.079 --> 00:27:56.880
