00:40:03.080 --> 00:40:03.560
Well, that's great.

00:40:03.560 --> 00:40:06.560
And I really liked how you bring up the point of like identifying each other's

00:40:06.560 --> 00:40:12.520
strengths, um, and, um, using that to kind of prioritize who can help with what.

00:40:12.520 --> 00:40:13.120
So thanks.

